snippet.title: It had everything to be a good PSX horror game, but... - The Bus
snippet.description:
Support our project on: http://www.patreon.com/5mg
Download FREE and more: https://www.5mgsite.com/post/the-bus-it-had-everything-to-be-a-good-psx-horror-game-but

The Bus is a short horror PSX game developed by Jacob Jazz where you play as someone who has his bike stolen and needs to go to work by bus on a rainy night. However, something dark happens. The Bus is the epilogue to Tamarindo's Freankin Dinner.

#indiegames #indiegame
